<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I managed to take Babbinsbort this weekend and complete the quest for the Gauntlets.<BR>
Just to let everyone know, I am a 25th season Cleric and that little gnome necro conned<BR>
black "white" to me. His spawn time has been greatly reduced as I'm sure many of us<BR>
are extremely happy about.  I and 2 friends quickly, though, not painlessly, dispatched<BR>
the evil one and his pet.  With Enduring breath I obtained the second part of the quest<BR>
from EF and the most difficult part was truly coming up with the 105pp for the bar and <BR>
then getting it enchanted.<BR>
Great armor though, I'm enjoying them throughly.<BR>
<BR>
Leedar the Humble<BR>
