<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>His name is Babbinsport, and no he does NOT spawn in Beholders. He spawns in the third floor of Befallen. Not sure of the exact location, but go to www.kmrcs.com/eqcleric for more information.<BR>
