<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Stormystone</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-07 14:10:41</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>After camping for 25 spawns (7 hours 14 mins each) before they patched to make the quests easier, I killed Babbs. last night. he was sitting there waiting for me. Now this is the really cool part, these gloves are now my most important piece of armor. I was wearing bronze gloves (9AC) and as we know these have 10AC, but Im getting about 35AC more with them. I get a total of 50AC when i compare them to having no gloves at all. This is because of the 5AGI and that Im a dwarf. I know my Halfelf rogue doesnt get that huge a jump from 5AGI. Anyway, they were well worth the wait, Ill take the over splitpaw gloves (that have 2wis) any time.<BR>
<BR>
BTW Babbs was blue to me at 29 and if not for my back up he would have killed me.<BR>
<BR>
Stormystone Burningforge<BR>
Gathered Might of Sol. Ro<BR>
</font></td></tr></table>
