<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Cerick Grimstalker</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-03-27 10:22:36</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Babbinsbort spawns on the third floor of befallen, he is right through the door that is halfway blocked with rock, once threw go to the right wree u seen 3 paths, open door and walk in, he is to the left behind a pillar that is lying horizontal on the ground.  He is very nasty with his spells.  I was with a lvl 28 and lvl 29 necro and we were fine other than the dots hurt a bit, but i am very sure u can not solo him unless around lvl 30 or so if not higher, I had to jump down the well last night and save my friend  (lvl 26 shadow knight)  who was virtually dead when i got there, good luck on finding him, i have only seen him 3 times in the last week and i have been in befallen every day of the week trying to camp gynok for his ring.  <BR>
<BR>
Cerick Grimstalker <BR>
cleric of the 26th life</font></td></tr></table>
